title: perfect mutual simulation hypothesis
pid: c8b26e4e-9ab0-41f2-940d-24fcc30fb942
body: |2-
  Everything running the calculation that every other thing most needs to know.
  ("Everything that would have reason for this at once.")

  Unfortunately, how each thing needs to interpret the others will depend on it and probably be non-obvious from the outside. That is, the reasons for simulation are as opaque as in the normal simulation hypothesis.
misc:
- Had_ID_Before_Import
